Well, straight from VW is a relative term. The Riviera conversion was
done in the USA rather than in Germany like the Westfalia. Also, I
think Riviera was a contract with VoA, so it's not really straight
from VW. It's like an independent camper conversion distributed by VW
dealers in the US.

